Class CustomerVisitHistory

  • java.lang.Object
    • CustomerVisitHistory
  • public class CustomerVisitHistory
extends java.lang.Object
    CustomerVisitHisotry class is to process the customer's visit history data so that It can be used in the program for other purpose. A CustomerVisitHistory object should contain the following private members: String customer_name - The name of the customer of the visit history, Localdatetime visitdatetime - The date and time of the visit history, Shop - The shop name of the visit history **formatter is a DateTimeFormatter object with the DateTimeFomart of ("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss") so that the date and time will be in this format.
